summary: The best way to start an adventure: a place to sleep with a storing chest, nothing else!
descriptionHtml:
[color=yellow][b]Description:[/b][/color]

Bored by huge and rich player homes, i have added a small tent just west of Whiterun.
The best way to start an adventure: a place to sleep with a storing chest, nothing else! (Barrels are set as respawn).
Have working map marker.

An italian version is available.

Take a look at [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/28484/?tab=3&navtag=%2Fajax%2Fmodimages%2F%3Fuser%3D0%26id%3D28484]Starter tent[/url], also featured on G.E.M.S.!


[color=yellow][b]Compatibilty:[/b][/color]

Everything, except mods that change same cell.


[color=yellow][b]My other mods:[/b][/color]

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/users/3271584/?tb=mods&pUp=1]Check all of them here[/url]
